reviewText: There are movies for all ages. I enjoyed watching them along with 5 and 10 year old. Don't have to just watch at Christmas.
Title: 10 Film Kid's Holiday Collector Set

reviewText: These are ok movies for the holidays.  They aren't great but they are an option of some new things to watch w/ the kids at the holidays...Also, they are super cheap so there is your combination...ok movies and super cheap prices, if you like that, your all set!
Title: 10 Film Kid's Holiday Collector Set

reviewText: For $5 I bought this DVD not expecting it to be 'amazing'. To be honest, the DVD is definitly not 'wow' factor but it is a cute dvd. My almost 3 year old loves it even when I was iffy of the quality. There are several shows on there and my daughter loved a few. For $5 I knew I shouldn't expect much.
Title: 10 Film Kid's Holiday Collector Set

reviewText: Grandkids loved it! A few classic Christmas movies with new ones also. Puts everyone in a holiday mood no matter your age.
Title: 10 Film Kid's Holiday Collector Set

reviewText: We were going to wait to give this to my son for christmas, however we did not. My son likes 4 out 10 of the movies on here. I only  can tolerate the 1st one. The last 6 are put together into a cartoon catergory.
Title: 10 Film Kid's Holiday Collector Set

reviewText: This is a nice collection of movies that the whole family can enjoy and watch together without worrying about the content and language for the holiday.
Title: 10 Film Kid's Holiday Collector Set

reviewText: I loved the holiday collection, and in good conditions, thank you, I love Christmas, so this worked out well for me
Title: 10 Film Kid's Holiday Collector Set

reviewText: This was bought to replace the one my Mother-in-law bought for the kids.  The kids love all the movies on it and it nice to see some of the older Christmas cartoons as one of the options to watch.
Title: 10 Film Kid's Holiday Collector Set
